<html><head><title>Home ministry’s AI vision: Predictive policing, dark web monitoring, and end of mule accounts</title></head><body><article><h1>Home ministry’s AI vision: Predictive policing, dark web monitoring, and end of mule accounts</h1><p>A parliamentary report shows how the MHA is utilising the expertise of IIT Bombay and the RBI to develop an AI-driven security system that tracks everything from dark web phishing to document forgery.</p><p>Reported by Autonomous Discovery - Cybercrime And Abuse AI</p></article></body></html>